metadata.name: Bye Bed-Stuy Gift
metadata.description:
Byeeee is a sculpture street art project that I started in 2005 before I left San Diego as a way to say bye. Thousands have been made by hand and placed in over 70 cities around the world. Since this project has always been about giving, there's no better way to begin than by offering my first NFT as a free claim. 

Map Link: https://goo.gl/maps/hpSPxiHPDaeTBwHH6  
If you're in New York, the sculpture might still be there for you to take! 

Holders of this will receive something special in 2023. 

I'll be dropping 1/1s of favorites and new ones as I go. Some will not include a map link.

Iâ€™ll be doing this until my final bye.
